          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Nine pieces of highly enriched 68Zn (>98%) metal",
                "foils were irradiated to obtain cross-sections using",
                "the stacked-foil technique. All foils were subjected",
                "to high efficiency radiochemical separation before",
                "the activity measurements."
